    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082350/extras/de6ed24c1ea949ebcabf1df1073ddc82.avif?t=1772069079\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082350/extras_big/de6ed24c1ea949ebcabf1df1073ddc82.avif?t=1772069079 width=800 height=57 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入文明血迹斑斑的废墟，《末日生存》是一款无情的俯视角roguelike游戏，将你置身于一个残酷的后末日世界中心。受动作roguelike类型启发，这款游戏提供了一个紧张且不断变化的战场，在这里，生存以秒计，危险无处不在。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082350/extras/3015acd1faedfcd51defb8f25efd905a.poster.avif?t=1772069079\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082350/extras/3015acd1faedfcd51defb8f25efd905a.webm?t=1772069079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082350/extras/3015acd1faedfcd51defb8f25efd905a.mp4?t=1772069079\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082350/extras/3711c5341b047d78df1451c8ac4dd7be.avif?t=1772069079\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082350/extras_big/3711c5341b047d78df1451c8ac4dd7be.avif?t=1772069079 width=800 height=57 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人类已灭绝。一种致命病毒从秘密实验室的深处泄露。一个又一个城市、一个又一个国家相继沦陷。在这个充满变异怪物的新现实中，你是少数幸存者之一。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在一个被可怕僵尸末日摧毁的世界中。你必须穿越各种环境，包括废弃的城镇和高度安全的实验室，以揭开疫情爆发背后的秘密。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082350/extras/3aae164bf541a58c9a127d7adc305e1f.avif?t=1772069079\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082350/extras_big/3aae164bf541a58c9a127d7adc305e1f.avif?t=1772069079 width=800 height=57 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>无情的群体战斗：</strong> 与无尽的变异体、僵尸和噩梦般的怪物群进行快节奏的战斗。它们的数量不断增长，力量不断增强，犹豫就意味着死亡。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>俯视射击玩法：</strong> 从战略视角享受战场的刺激，抵御无情的僵尸浪潮。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>广泛致命武器库：</strong> 从多种近战武器、枪械和道具中进行选择，以创造自己的游戏风格。解锁并升级你的装备，打造无敌配置。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>角色小队：</strong> 解锁具有特殊能力的新幸存者，改变游戏玩法，获得另一种体验。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>迷人的背景故事：</strong> 通过幸存者的笔记……或死者的笔记……揭示灾难发生的起源。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多样化的环境：</strong> 探索不同的地点，每个地点都有独特的危险，并隐藏着一个戏剧性的故事。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>令人屏息的恐怖体验：</strong> 置身于令人毛骨悚然的氛围中，由令人毛骨悚然的视觉和音效增强。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082350/extras/be23ab8299c0a3b356133abab569f7d7.avif?t=1772069079\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082350/extras_big/be23ab8299c0a3b356133abab569f7d7.avif?t=1772069079 width=800 height=57 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >末日无情。弱者灭亡，强者生存——但能坚持多久？拿起武器，面对成群的敌人，证明你有能力在地狱般的末日中存活下来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有第二次机会。没有安全区。只有鲜血、钢铁，以及不懈的生存斗争。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>准备好自己。末日已经开始…</strong></p>",
